The $R^{OV}_7$ transformation represents changes in vantage perspective in the 7D space. It can be written in block form as:
\begin{equation}
R^{OV}_7 = \begin{pmatrix} 
R_{00} & R_{0S} \\
R_{S0} & R_{SS}
\end{pmatrix}
