\subsubsection{Universal Time Block}
The universal time component $R_{00}$ is:
\begin{equation}
R_{00} = \cos\alpha_x + \cos\delta_x + \cos\alpha_y + \cos\delta_y + \cos\alpha_z + \cos\delta_z
