where $\varphi_i = \sqrt{\alpha_i^2 + \delta_i^2}$.

The inter-sector blocks $R_{(i,j)}$ (for $i \neq j$) contain cross-coupling terms with effective angles $\psi_{ij} = \kappa_{ij}(\hat{n}_{ij} \cdot \vec{\beta})$.

