\subsection{Tilt Angles and Orbital Parameters}

The OXI framework's tilt angles map to orbital parameters as:

\begin{equation}
\alpha_{ij} = \frac{1}{2}\tan^{-1}\left(\frac{2\beta_{ij}}{1-\beta_{ij}^2}\right)
